item.title: GSoC last week, GNOME final report! :)
item.description: It’s been a while since my last post just after GUADEC. I’ve lost some time in August due moving to a new place in Campinas with two friends of mine. It was three weeks ago and I’m still feeling tired (I’m taking some time to get used with this new place). Since then, I’m working on grilo-plugins and this post is all about what I’ve accomplished and what are the next steps after GSoC.
